---
title: Silky Peanut-Ginger Tofu Noodles with Linguine and Veggies
description: Peanut butter lovers, rejoice! The nutty aroma and subtle creaminess of peanut butter boost this deeply delicious sauce that we're using to coat slurpy noodles, crumbled tofu and crisp vegetables.

